## Limitations

- Fixture returns are deterministic and small; they are diagnostic inputs, not proof of profitability.
- Signal usefulness metrics check follow-through in fixture data only.
- A signal can affect simulation only when `available_from` is on or before the decision date.
- The policy output is a review simulation and must not be interpreted as live trading advice.
